<template>
  <v-carousel
    height="100vh"
  >
    <v-carousel-item
      v-for="(item,i) in items"
      :key="i"
      :src="item.src"
      reverse-transition="fade-transition"
      transition="fade-transition"
    ></v-carousel-item>
  </v-carousel>
</template>

  

<script>
  export default {
    data () {
      return {
        items: [
          {
            src: "https://64.media.tumblr.com/3f6b024306b0a3dcf2328dc181105f1e/b5b0c0e388770894-d4/s540x810/27f9f92af37d0d36bf63bb0381f88fcfa84d3b3a.gif",
          },
          {
            src: 'https://c.tenor.com/VrzXhtoSwcsAAAAd/hacker-typing.gif',
          },
          {
            src: 'https://c.tenor.com/CWgfFh7ozHkAAAAC/rick-astly-rick-rolled.gif',
          },
          {
            src: 'https://c.tenor.com/Xrt-ty39PfEAAAAC/elon-musk-smoke.gif',
          },
        ],
      }
    },
  }
</script>
